    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>    Parser element for quoted strings.

    Simple usage examples:
    &gt;&gt;&gt; from dragonfly.parser import Parser
    &gt;&gt;&gt; parser = Parser(Integer())
    &gt;&gt;&gt; parser.parse(&quot;0&quot;)
    0
    &gt;&gt;&gt; parser.parse(&quot;+0&quot;)
    0
    &gt;&gt;&gt; parser.parse(&quot;-000&quot;)
    0
    &gt;&gt;&gt; parser.parse(&quot;1234&quot;)
    1234
    &gt;&gt;&gt; parser.parse(&quot;+001234&quot;)
    1234
    &gt;&gt;&gt; parser.parse(&quot;-001234&quot;)
    -1234</verbatim> </para>    </detaileddescription>
